      ],
      "text": "Sozin's dragon was a blue dragon that Fire Lord Sozin used as a mount and his animal companion. As vicious as his master, Sozin's dragon was able to fly great distances at fast speeds."
    },
    {
      "body": "In 12 ${link_0}, Sozin used his dragon to cross the hundred miles that separated the ${link_1} and ${link_2} in order to help his ${link_3} battle the erupting volcanoes that threatened to engulf the island in fire. When Roku was fainting from the poisonous volcanic gases, Sozin's dragon swooped in and saved only his master, while the pyroclastic flow swept over the ${link_4} and ${link_5}, killing them both.",
